data.description: Mid-Century home on a 6,700 sqft Corner Lot. Beautifully Restored in 2015 with a Brand-New Roof, Fresh Stucco, and Updated Windows. The original Oak floors have been masterfully refinished, lending timeless elegance to the entire home. The Custom Kitchen boasts Quartz countertops, a Carrara Marble backsplash, and Stainless Steel Appliances. The bathroom showcases a Custom Shower and floor tile, complemented by a new vanity featuring a Quartz countertop. Step outside to the generous patio adorned with a pergola, lush lawn, and thoughtfully landscaped surroundings with irrigation. The sizable side yard offers gated access from the street, providing ample space for RV or boat storage, or add and ADU for extra rental income.
